                  <p>
                    <b>Adjust the TRND requirement for the Trendering Private telegram group</b>
                    <br />
                    <small class="text-gray-500">0xf0b699A8559A3fFAf72f1525aBe14CebcD1De5Ed</small>
                  </p>

                  <p>
                    At the time of creating this TIP there are 396 members in the Trendering Private telegram group. While the interest in the group is definitely a positive sign, in the long run it may not be sustainable. Therefore, I propose an adjustment mechanism to the TRND requirement that verifies group members, to maintain group's quality and exclusivity.
                  </p>

                  <p>
                    The adjustment mechanism, codenamed "300 Spartans", would work as follows: the amount of members in the group is checked once a day and if the amount is higher than 300, the TRND requirement is increased by 1 token. This check repeats every day and the TRND requirement continues to increase daily until there are 300 members in the group.
                  </p>

                  <p>
                    C.
                  </p>

